info.name: NIR Sandbox
info.description:
## About this Collection Each Postman "request" corresponds to an endpoint on NIR, and a selection of examples have been provided for each of them. Each example request is accompanied by an expected response. ## NIR Sandbox The NIR Sandbox does not require MTLS or WS-Security headers (as opposed to the strict security requirements in place on the Live environment). All test data and downstream systems are provided using mocks and simulators. ## Examples Test data has been set up to demonstrate the following scenarios: | **Scenario** | **Simulator 1 -** urn:oid:1.2.34.567.8.1 | Simulator 2 - urn:oid:1.2.34.567.8.2 | Postman Collection Example | | --- | --- | --- | --- | | Query a single document for a single patient from a single network | Patient Id: 9694116422 | | Single Document From A Single Network (PDF) | | Query multiple documents for a single patient from a single network | Patient Id: 9898841141 | | Multiple Documents From A Single Network (PDF, DICOM) | | Query multiple documents for a single patient across multiple network | Patient Id: 9932549118 | Patient Id: 9932549118 | Documents From Multiple Networks (PDF, DICOM) | | Retrieve a single document from a single network | Patient Id: 9932549118
